The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 US beat Serbia 2-1

Perth: The United States defeated Serbia and Montenegro 2-1 at the Hopman Cup on Sunday, after Lisa Raymond lost 6-2, 6-4 to Ana Ivanovic. 

Taylor Dent put the Americans level by outplaying Novak Djokovic 6-1, 6-4, and then teamed with Raymond to win the mixed doubles 7-6, 6-2. 

Ivanovic dominated Raymond, overpowering her from the baseline and striking blistering returns. (Reuters) 




